          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " had a new box to unveil. Presenting their 440 for the first time during the summer of 1988, with Lamborghini’s ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
