          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " carving a contemporary path for car design, Volvo counteracted all that automotive adrenaline with a solid injection of colourless and underwhelming banality. At least, so time’s onward march may have you believe.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
